{"type":null,"faqId":12582,"title":"C8813（G510）  如何设置自选音乐为来电/短信铃音?","answer":"<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">1. 进入设置-&gt;声音-&gt;手机铃，修改来电铃声。</span><br />\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">2. 进入设置-&gt;声音-&gt;通知铃声-&gt;消息通知铃声，修改短信铃声。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=34712\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">3. 在文件管理中长按一个选中的音乐文件，弹出菜单后选择设置为-&gt;手机铃声/通知铃</span><br />\n<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">声。</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=34713\" alt=\"\" /></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">4. 手机铃声另外设置方法：进入音乐选择并长按任意一首歌曲设为铃声。</span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=34714\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3464","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1399512940000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":111,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"C8813（G510）","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}